    "page.support.text": "We provide comprehensive technical support for power transformer design, manufacturing, and maintenance. Our team of experienced engineers is available to assist with troubleshooting, diagnostics, and on-site consultation. Whether you need help with routine maintenance planning, emergency fault analysis, or optimizing transformer performance, we offer tailored solutions to keep your equipment running reliably and efficiently.",
